OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782251281
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cconspiracy to murder after fatal
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThree people arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder following the death of a man in
OL,9,FNewcastle have been released on police
OL,10,Fbail, as detectives made three further
OL,11,Farrests.
OL,13,FEmergency services were called to
OL,14,FShields Road in Byker at around 7.25pm
OL,15,Fon Tuesday (16 June) after reports of
OL,16,Fan assault.
OL,18,FA man in his 20s suffered serious
OL,19,Finjuries and was taken to hospital,
OL,20,Fwhere he later died.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
