CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782251281
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cconspiracy to murder after fatal
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police said the victim's
OL,8,Finjuries were consistent with being
OL,9,Fcaused by a bladed article.
OL,11,FTwo men aged 24 and 22, and a 16-year-
OL,12,Fold boy, were arrested on suspicion of
OL,13,Fmurder but police have now confirmed
OL,14,Fthey have been released on bail.
OL,16,FThree more people ` two men aged 40
OL,17,Fand 33, and a 16-year-old boy ` were
OL,18,Flater arrested in the Walker area on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to murder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
