CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782251281
OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cconspiracy to murder after fatal
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FA Northumbria Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "A murder investigation remains
OL,9,Fongoing after a man sadly died
OL,10,Ffollowing a suspected assault in Byker
OL,11,Fon Tuesday.
OL,13,F"Three people ` two men aged 24 and
OL,14,F22, and a boy aged 16 ` were arrested
OL,15,Fon suspicion of murder. They have
OL,16,Fsince been released on police bail,
OL,17,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
