OL,3,CThree arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cconspiracy to murder after fatal
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,F"Three more people ` two men aged 40
OL,8,Fand 33, and a boy aged 16 ` were later
OL,9,Farrested in the Walker area on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to murder."
OL,12,FOfficers remain in the Byker and
OL,13,FWalker areas carrying out enquiries
OL,14,Fand offering reassurance to the public.
